# This is NOT the Next.js you know

This project uses **Next.js 16** with breaking changes — APIs, conventions, and file structure may differ from older docs or model training data.

- Before changing routing, data fetching, or config, read the relevant guide in **`node_modules/next/dist/docs/`** (or the official Next.js docs for your installed version).
- Heed deprecation notices and verify APIs against the installed package, not memory.
